{"tid":1242021,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實大家知唔知咩叫deadline","createTime":"2019-06-19T02:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T05:30:03.000Z","uid":182792,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4a7f39ed27c09fb9078cf688fee61f71ebe254b7","tid":1242021,"uid":182792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:11:54.000Z","msg":"deadline即係死線呀<br />\n係真係要有明顯嘅進一步行動呀<br />\n仲喺度講咩等23號/71遊行<br />\n最撚廢就係咩等下一屆投票<br />\n人哋識dq 又有分組點票 功能組別  基本上建制都未必一定會輸<br />\n何況去到下一屆之前已經乜都過曬啦<br />\n咁set deadline嚟把撚呀<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">可以瘋狂延期嘅deadline仲叫唔叫deadline？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好喺度講埋啲咩掟紙飛機 寫訴求<br />\n作用仲廢撚過連儂牆<br />\n政府根本wfc<br />\n<br />\n仲有人鏈唔反抗畀狗推撞<br />\n發夢班義士如果真係要喺前面聽你班友講唔反抗<br />\n最後畀狗塔曬返去  到時唔用警棍兜頭扑<br />\n就咁拉都拉散你啦<br />\n係吸引到國際注視呀<br />\n但係義士係畀你哋當死士咁用㗎咩<br />\n何況班狗冇人性嘅事實國際間唔知咩？  做多幾多次都係一樣<br />\n<br />\n乜嘢叫行動升級呀？<br />\n搞埋啲嘢仲廢過612咁有乜用<br />\n唔好喺度政治潔癖拎光環啦"},{"pid":"3b11ca360c4a1d35ecc9e81e9c354cc5b4ab8875","tid":1242021,"uid":182792,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:14:52.000Z","msg":"見到啲人喺度拖拖拖就嬲<br />\nset條deadline 同冇set deadline係冇分別<br />\n咁政府仲驚條撚咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56de7be1aac73c4799f700916a6628c8fbfd57ea","tid":1242021,"uid":182792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:17:11.000Z","msg":"求幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82445be8432feb51c0d600d97bc61dbec077182a","tid":1242021,"uid":156623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:18:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"744aaf1d24932d26ba3d2d8174f99ff7d13d0ad8","tid":1242021,"uid":203537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:22:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d46cfa037919c7d69dae515da4f5b5298b72a016","tid":1242021,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:23:12.000Z","msg":"<i